revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yagers}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yager'' is the 4766<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 7427 individuals.
